      "description": "[[/attack extended]]. [[/damage average extended]]. If the target is a creature, it is subjected to the following effect.\n\nConstitution Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=F0T3hYR3EtUEMhvs]].\n\nFirst Failure: The target has the &amp;Reference[Poisoned apply=false] condition. While Poisoned, the target's Hit Point maximum doesn't return to normal when finishing a Long Rest, and it repeats the save every 24 hours that elapse, ending the effect on itself on a success.\n\nSubsequent Failures: The Poisoned target's Hit Point maximum decreases by 5 ([[/r 1d10]]).",
